title: Commercial Forest Hunting Lands (Private Forest Land)
description: Commercial Forests Open to Hunting includes lands managed by private citizens in agreement with the Michigan Department of Natural Resources that are open to public hunting. Please double check with the appropriate agency for specific rules, regulations, and restrictions.

title: Metropolitan Planning Organizations (MPO)
description: Metropolitan Planning Organizations (MPO) are boundaries that define specific urbanized areas along with adjacent municipalities that are accepted into the MPO. MPOs serve as localized areas for transportation planning and forecasting traffic demand models. Please see the?MDOT Metadata Form?for additional information.?Update Cycle: The MPO boundaries are updated every census release. They were last updated after the 2010 census.Coverage: This layer is complete in its coverage of all State of Michigan Metropolitan Planning Organizations.Contact:?Pam Boyd  John Lanum
